citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:10 pm on 06-
October-20.
The inspector arrived at the facility at 2:10 pm and honked the car horn multiple times. The inspector also called the
phone number, but the voicemail box was full and a message could not be left. The inspector waited 30 minutes and then
left the facility.
End Section
